{
  "stem": "4967.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, my late uncle and auntie, [NON-ENGLISH] from my father's side, and his wife and his two children in the bunker, a hideout under the floor in the house, and the mother, and they were burned alive, or blew up alive.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they blew up house to house for days.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we saw things are banding together.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my father was running around on the roof, and, look, they blow up this and this, and they're coming closer to us.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What can we do?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We got nowhere to hide ourselves.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he find other people moving to a certain direction, certain people who were wealthy people in our block where we've stayed.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you find out that in this [NON-ENGLISH], this place where they used to de-louse the people, used to be showers steam, used to kill the lice, [INAUDIBLE], whatever it is, people going in through the oven with a prearranged [NON-ENGLISH], a hideout place.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So he come to us and says, let's go, we find a hideout place.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we come, but they wouldn't let us in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Say, you got gold, you got diamonds, you got money.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He says, I got nothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I got my life.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "If you don't let us in, you have no your life and not our life, because the Germans will find us any minute here.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It's a matter of 10 or 15 minutes the Germans will be us, and you will not manage to close the doors, because we're going to stay here.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It's a matter of life and death for you and for us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So they went in there to discuss, the elders, and they let us in.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a dig out place under the foundations of this big block, and the insulation was very bad.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
